The Telegraph - Calcutta : Sports

 Real close in on Ballack, Robben 

Madrid: Real Madrid are close to signing Germany midfielder Michael Ballack and Netherlands winger Arjen Robben from Chelsea, Spanish media reported on Saturday. 

A top radio programme and leading sports dailies said the two internationals could move to Madrid for a total of euro 40 million. (AGENCIES) 




